&lt;h4 class=&quot;pse-p pse-h4&quot;&gt;Co oznaczają kontrolki LED?&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;pse-grid pse-div&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;column column-2 pse-div&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;pse-p pse-h4 pse-align-center&quot;&gt;Błąd&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;pse-figure pse-align-center outset-both&quot; style=&quot;max-width:121px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/img/pshoweditor/2125726299.thumbnail.png&quot; class=&quot;pse-img&quot; width=&quot;121&quot; height=&quot;121&quot; style=&quot;width:121px;max-width:121px;&quot; alt=&quot;2125726299.thumbnail.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;pse-p pse-align-center&quot;&gt;&lt;b class=&quot;pse-b&quot;&gt;Czerwona&lt;/b&gt; kontrolka informuje o &lt;b class=&quot;pse-b&quot;&gt;wykrytym uszkodzeniu&lt;/b&gt; lub &lt;b class=&quot;pse-b&quot;&gt;przeciążeniu&lt;/b&gt; (jeśli aktywny jest system Compatec/Compamatic)&lt;/p&gt;
